I used to pay the 5p per pelt for MQ pelts.  Then I realized I was just being stupid and stopped.  I'll snatch em up in a heartbeat if I see em for 1pp or sometimes even 2pp.  Still a bit high IMO, but at that point it is easier to get the pp than to get the pelts myself.  That is what it is all about; how easy is it to get the pp vs to get the items.  For those of high enough level, 5pp is easier to get than 1 pelt. <p>Mithlin Lussarrna<BR>
